###############################################################
##                                                           ##
## This is the maxiPago! integration library in PHP that     ##
## allows you to use all of the platform's functions.        ##
##                                                           ##
##    METHODS                                                ##
##                                                           ##
## You must import the contents of the 'includes' folder to  ##
## be able to execute the methods below:                     ##
##                                                           ##
##  - Credit Card Transactions                               ##
##    -- Authorization                                       ##
##    -- Capture                                             ##
##    -- Sale (Authorization+Capture)                        ##
##    -- Token Authorization (saved card)                    ##
##    -- Token Sale (saved card)                             ##
##    -- Void (until 11:59pm of the same day)                ##
##    -- Refund                                              ##
##                                                           ##	  
##  - Recurring Transactions                                 ##
##  -- Create new recurring credit card billing              ##
##                                                           ##	
##  - Boleto Transactions                                    ##
##  -- Create new boleto                                     ##
##                                                           ##	
##  - Reports                                                ##
##  -- Query one single transaction                          ##
##  -- Query a list of transactions                          ##
##  -- Flip through pages of a transaction list              ##
##  -- Query a pending report                                ##
##                                                           ##	
##  - Customer Profile                                       ##
##  -- Create a profile                                      ##
##  -- Update a profile                                      ##
##  -- Remove a profile                                      ##
##  -- Add a credit card                                     ##
##  -- Remove a credit card                                  ##
##                                                           ##	
## Within each folder you will find examples for the methods ##
##  listed above.                                            ##
##                                                           ##
##    ENVIRONMENT                                            ##
##                                                           ##	
## To determine the environment the transactions will be     ##
## sent to you need to set the API URL. Alls the URLs can be ##
## found in our documentation (link below)                   ##           
##                                                           ##   
##    DOCUMENTATION                                          ##
##                                                           ##   
## For more information please refer to our documentation at ##
## http://www.maxipago.com/docs/maxiPago_API_Latest.pdf or   ##
## contact us at support@maxipago.com                        ##
##                                                           ##
###############################################################